issue.title: AdGuard extension making Firefox too slow/laggy
issue.body:
### Prerequisites

- [X] This site DOES NOT contains sexually explicit material, otherwise use [NSFW-specific form](./new?template=bug_report_NSFW.yml);
- [X] Filters were updated before reproducing an issue;
- [X] AdGuard product version is up-to-date;
- [X] Browser version is up-to-date;
- [X] If the site or app is broken, disabling AdGuard protection resolves an issue.

### What product do you use?

AdGuard Browser Extension

### AdGuard version

4.0.204

### What type of problem have you encountered?

Website or app doesn't work properly

### Which browser(s) do you use?

Firefox

### Which device do you use?

Desktop

### Where is the problem encountered?

https://translate.google.com/

### What filters do you have enabled?

AdGuard Base filter

### What Stealth Mode options do you have enabled?

_No response_

### Add your comment and screenshots

AdGuard is making translate.google.com too slow, I cannot reproduce with similar add-on "uBlock Origin".

My video proving this on fresh firefox profile
https://streamable.com/9o7bzz
![image3](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/62249282/182747236-853b1610-7
![picture](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/62249282/182747514-363bb1d5-8956-4419-80bc-fc55b834a027.png)
6dd-430c-92ca-0724ce4563a1.png)

![picture](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/62249282/182747399-4e1e000b-36d8-411f-b15f-10c0f4cbb360.png)

I hope you can reproduce it, but if you cant, any idea what it could be?
